title: paragraph 5(2) (as amended by section 4 of the Milk (Regulation of Supply(
heading: 2. 24th September 2024 is prescribed as an election day for producer
text_raw:
2. 24th September 2024 is prescribed as an election day for producer 

members of the National Milk Agency. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

26 June, 2024. 

CHARLIE MCCONALOGUE, 

Minister for Agriculture, Food and the Marine. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 12th July, 2024. 

 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 EXPLANATORY NOTE 

[ ] 3 

(This note is not part of the instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation.) 

The purpose of these Regulations is to fix the 24th September 2024 as an election 
day for producer members of the National Milk Agency.
